OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and largely dry day.
OL,6,FCloudier in the morning with just the
OL,7,Fslight chance of an isolated light
OL,8,Fshower. Increasingly sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping through the day. Breezy
OL,10,Fwith occasional strong winds on
OL,11,Fnorthern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with some bright or sunny
OL,14,Fspells in the evening. It will stay
OL,15,Fdry overnight with increasing clear
OL,16,Fspells developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
