OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FDry, warm and bright or sunny
OL,6,Fthrough much of the day. Sunshine
OL,7,Fturning hazier in the afternoon as
OL,8,Fcloud spreads east. Chance of the odd
OL,9,Fspot of rain in evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable period but often dry and
OL,13,Fbright with sunny spells. Some patchy
OL,14,Frain or a few showers possible at
OL,15,Ftimes, mainly in the west.
